   <pb facs="2"/>
   <head>To the courteous Reader.</head>
   <p>
      <hi>COurteous Reader,</hi> in these sub<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>sequent pages, excuse I pray thee, the shortnesse of the matter, and the rudenesse of the style, and attribute that to my cal<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>ling, being long a Souldiour; and this to my education, which hath beene more out of my native Countrie than in it, and make thy use of the matter which I have set downe for thy well, rather than to censure the defect of my language. Farewell.</p>
